<i>adverb</i>: 한결같이 [한결가치], 하나같이 [하나가치], 일정히 [일쩡히], 가지런히 [가지런히] <br>
<ul style="list-style-type:square">
<li><i>adverb</i><br>
<dt>한결같이 [한결가치]</dt><br>
<dd>1. constantly; unchangingly; consistently</dd><br>
<dd>처음부터 끝까지 변함없이 똑같이.</dd><br>
<dd>In a manner of being the same as ever from the beginning to the end.</dd><br>
<dd>2. uniformly; in unison; evenly</dd><br>
<dd>여럿이 모두 똑같아서 마치 하나와 같이.</dd><br>
<dd>In a manner in which many people behave the same way, as if they were one.</dd><br>
<dt>하나같이 [하나가치]</dt><br>
<dd>uniformly; without exception</dd><br>
<dd>모두가 조금도 다른 데가 없이 꼭 같이.</dd><br>
<dd>In such a manner that two or more persons or things are not a bit different from each other in appearance, reaction, etc.</dd><br>
<dt>일정히 [일쩡히]</dt><br>
<dd>1. uniformly</dd><br>
<dd>여럿의 크기, 모양, 시간, 범위 등이 하나로 정해져서 똑같이.</dd><br>
<dd>In the state of several things being the same in size, shape, temporal period, range, etc.</dd><br>
<dd>2. constantly</dd><br>
<dd>여럿의 양, 성질, 상태, 계획 등이 변하지 않고 한결같이.</dd><br>
<dd>In the state of an amount, quality, state, plan, etc., being unchanging.</dd><br>
<dd>3. regularly; systematically</dd><br>
<dd>전체적인 흐름이나 절차가 규칙적으로.</dd><br>
<dd>In the state of an overall flow or procedure being regular.</dd><br>
<dt>가지런히 [가지런히]</dt><br>
<dd>uniformly</dd><br>
<dd>크기나 모양이 큰 차이가 없이 고르고 나란히.</dd><br>
<dd>In a uniform manner without great difference, in size or shape.</dd><br>
</li>
</ul>